  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/1f11e45acbe0b430382500bb9876e187.poster.avif?t=1748727944\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/1f11e45acbe0b430382500bb9876e187.webm?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/1f11e45acbe0b430382500bb9876e187.mp4?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Fall\" was created by Tan Haoxiang, the individual game developer of \"The Jiang Si\", \"The Jiang Si 2: Curse of Soul\", and \"Star Quest\",\"Fall\" is a top-down modern zombie-style meat pigeon action game that presents players with a challenging and surprising post-apocalyptic  this game, you will play as a survivor, shuttling through the ruins of a city overrun by zombies, exploring unknown areas, collecting resources, strengthening yourself, and fighting life and death with various forms of zombies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rich weapons and equipment</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/51cf82cac1d54fec57d36618fa169736.poster.avif?t=1748727944\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/51cf82cac1d54fec57d36618fa169736.webm?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/51cf82cac1d54fec57d36618fa169736.mp4?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From automatic rifles to grenade launchers, from simple police drones to high-tech artificial intelligence characters, the game provides a diverse selection of weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thrilling combat system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/faa0031af7dc944e48308c6ec6290522.poster.avif?t=1748727944\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/faa0031af7dc944e48308c6ec6290522.webm?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/faa0031af7dc944e48308c6ec6290522.mp4?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Facing hordes of zombies, players need to use strategies and skills to take advantage of the environment and force them to make wise choices between attack and survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse types of zombies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/8a616fc7ed68a7f2cac8fe007b0825a0.poster.avif?t=1748727944\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/8a616fc7ed68a7f2cac8fe007b0825a0.webm?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/8a616fc7ed68a7f2cac8fe007b0825a0.mp4?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From ordinary zombies to mutants with special abilities, players will face different challenges.Some zombies are extremely fast, while others have strong attack power, forcing players to constantly adjust their tactics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story-driven background</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/5769467105b89252ff6cd088d2a055a2.poster.avif?t=1748727944\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/5769467105b89252ff6cd088d2a055a2.webm?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/5769467105b89252ff6cd088d2a055a2.mp4?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Although the game is mainly in the Rogue-like mode, there is a fascinating story hidden behind it.As the game progresses, players will gradually uncover the reasons behind the end of the world and the possible path to redemption.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Fall\" is not only a game that tests players' operational skills, but also a profound exploration of human nature, survival, and  each game, players will experience different stories and face different challenges, and every failure is for a stronger rebirth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Official communication group QQ of \"Fall\": 752209909</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/1f11e45acbe0b430382500bb9876e187.poster.avif?t=1748727944\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/1f11e45acbe0b430382500bb9876e187.webm?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/1f11e45acbe0b430382500bb9876e187.mp4?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Fall\" was created by Tan Haoxiang, the individual game developer of \"The Jiang Si\", \"The Jiang Si 2: Curse of Soul\", and \"Star Quest\",\"Fall\" is a top-down modern zombie-style meat pigeon action game that presents players with a challenging and surprising post-apocalyptic  this game, you will play as a survivor, shuttling through the ruins of a city overrun by zombies, exploring unknown areas, collecting resources, strengthening yourself, and fighting life and death with various forms of zombies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rich weapons and equipment</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/51cf82cac1d54fec57d36618fa169736.poster.avif?t=1748727944\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/51cf82cac1d54fec57d36618fa169736.webm?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/51cf82cac1d54fec57d36618fa169736.mp4?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From automatic rifles to grenade launchers, from simple police drones to high-tech artificial intelligence characters, the game provides a diverse selection of weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thrilling combat system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/faa0031af7dc944e48308c6ec6290522.poster.avif?t=1748727944\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/faa0031af7dc944e48308c6ec6290522.webm?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/faa0031af7dc944e48308c6ec6290522.mp4?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Facing hordes of zombies, players need to use strategies and skills to take advantage of the environment and force them to make wise choices between attack and survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse types of zombies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/8a616fc7ed68a7f2cac8fe007b0825a0.poster.avif?t=1748727944\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/8a616fc7ed68a7f2cac8fe007b0825a0.webm?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/8a616fc7ed68a7f2cac8fe007b0825a0.mp4?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From ordinary zombies to mutants with special abilities, players will face different challenges.Some zombies are extremely fast, while others have strong attack power, forcing players to constantly adjust their tactics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story-driven background</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/5769467105b89252ff6cd088d2a055a2.poster.avif?t=1748727944\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/5769467105b89252ff6cd088d2a055a2.webm?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705230/extras/5769467105b89252ff6cd088d2a055a2.mp4?t=1748727944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Although the game is mainly in the Rogue-like mode, there is a fascinating story hidden behind it.As the game progresses, players will gradually uncover the reasons behind the end of the world and the possible path to redemption.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Fall\" is not only a game that tests players' operational skills, but also a profound exploration of human nature, survival, and  each game, players will experience different stories and face different challenges, and every failure is for a stronger rebirth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Official communication group QQ of \"Fall\": 752209909</p>",
